Package: episcope
Title: Episcope: An Integrative Epigenomic Analysis Framework
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yaoxiang", "Li", , "yaoxiang@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Chunling", "Yi", , "chunling@example.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Robust and reproducible framework for epigenetic data analysis. It integrates functionalities for ChromHMM analysis, DNA methylation assessment, differentiation state profiling, paired ATAC-seq and RNA-seq analysis, and functional mapping to facilitate comprehensive epigenomic studies.
